{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "没有人迹的肮脏小巷。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "一名男子消失在了暗门后。\\n库格尔和海因瓦尔德\\n正在监视他的行动。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "又有一个人进去了……\\n这是第4个人了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "剩下的就是幕后主使了。\\n不到最后不现身，还真是谨慎。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "所以到现在都没能\\n抓住他们的狐狸尾巴。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "终于把他们逼入了绝境……\\n今天一定要抓住他们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "主张灭龙的异端集团。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "以教会的立场，\\n不能对他们的活动坐视不管。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "那是自然。那些家伙\\n不分青红皂白就攻击龙……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "都怪他们，附近小镇和村子都\\n受到龙的报复而深受其害。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "那才是他们的目的吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "他们想让人们把龙当作\\n会袭击人的危险猛兽。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "这次没有喊上尤蒂尔，\\n也是这个原因吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "算是吧。要是让他知道了，\\n一定会二话不说就来帮忙的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "但他原本\\n不该插手这种事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "那些正面挑衅教会的家伙，\\n让我们来对付就足够了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "一味盯着脚下，\\n就无法实现远大抱负。　\\n他应该着眼于后者，而不是前则。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "（这种地方居然也咬舌头吗……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "还没来……好闲啊。\\n话说库格尔……\\n“神”到底是什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "嗯？管这种情形叫太闲，\\n真是不懂你的脑回路……\\n更不懂你到底想问什么。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "很简单，\\n只是突然冒出的疑问。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "你们所信仰的“女神”是什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "如果她真的存在，那为什么会对\\n这些明显是异端的家伙放任不管？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "哼，好无聊的问题。\\n不过……好吧，姑且回答你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "女神可没有闲工夫\\n去管那种家伙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "她是从魔神手中拯救了世界、\\n值得后世敬仰的存在。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "她的威光遍及整个世界。\\n哪有空一个个惩罚恶人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "女神伊莉雅拯救了世界。\\n信徒们理所当然地这样认为。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "喂……你到底想说什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "我觉得现在正在追踪的\\n异端们的主张也很有意思。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "龙为了让自己成为至高无上的存在\\n而设立了教会……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "那些龙为了让教会笼络人心\\n而创造出了一位虚假的偶像……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "那正是女神伊莉雅。\\n所以一切都是龙妄图征服世界的阴谋，\\n大概就是这样吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "你这家伙……\\n还真敢对着异端审问官说这些。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "说这话的人要不是你，\\n我这斧头就直接让他闭嘴了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "我也不是真的相信\\n这种无凭无据的说法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "愚蠢至极。女神啊，\\n请制裁这天杀的无信仰者吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "如果这种假说是真的，\\n那为什么龙没有统治人类啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "看来女神伊莉雅实际存在的\\n这种观点是根深蒂固的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "当然。为了让人们了解女神的威光，\\n我才当了异端审问官。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "但是，就算……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "嗯？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "就算像你说的那样，女神并不存在，\\n我的初衷也不会变。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "现在拯救众人的\\n无疑就是伊莉雅教会，\\n还有身为女神使徒的祭司。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "这世上已经充满了女神的爱，\\n不必劳烦女神亲力亲为。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "今后教会也会谨遵女神教诲，\\n向弱者伸出援助之手。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "那正是女神\\n真实存在的证明吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "没错。但也有拒绝女神救赎、\\n只想满足一己私欲的狡诈家伙……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "对于那些无可救药的家伙，\\n我会亲手把他们送到女神尊前。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "这就是为什么我能自豪地称自己\\n为伊莉雅教会的异端审问官。\\n因为这对于我来说，就是真实存在的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "还真像你的作风呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "哎呀，刚才进去的人是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "看来主角终于到了，\\n可以开始开派对了呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "无聊的问答该告一段落了。\\n光靠讲道理，\\n女神的惩罚可不会降临。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "海因瓦尔德",
            "context": "那我倒想问问，\\n你所谓的惩罚要如何降临？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "这还用说，当然是借我之手。\\n敢违逆女神的家伙，\\n我会毫不留情地给予制裁！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "库格尔",
            "context": "要上了啊，搭档。\\n女神永远与我同在！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110281_01_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}